i## 用内核模块加速 Looking Glass		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i> 这段内容大都来自		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
h> https://looking-glass.io/docs/B6/module/	URL:https://looking-glass.io/docs/B6/module/	{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iLooking Glass 提供了一个内核模块，可以用于 IVSHMEM 共享内存设备，让		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iLooking Glass 能使用 DMA 技术高效地读取虚拟机画面，从而提高帧率。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i1. 安装 Linux 内核头文件和 DKMS，在 Arch Linux 上就是安装 `linux-headers`		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   和 `dkms` 两个包。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i2. 从 AUR 安装 `looking-glass-module-dkms`。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i3. 配置 Udev 规则：创建 `/etc/udev/rules.d/99-kvmfr.rules`，写入以下内		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   容：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     SUBSYSTEM=="kvmfr", OWNER="lantian", GROUP="kvm", MODE="0660"		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   将 `lantian` 替换成你自己的用户名。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i4. 配置内存大小：创建 `/etc/modprobe.d/looking-glass.conf`，写入以下内		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   容：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     # 这里的内存大小计算方法和虚拟机的 shmem 一项相同。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     options kvmfr static_size_mb=64		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i5. 开机自动加载模块：创建 `/etc/modules-load.d/looking-glass.conf`，写		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   入一行 `kvmfr`。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i6. 运行 `sudo modprobe kvmfr` 加载模块，此时 `/dev` 下会多出一个 `kvmfr0`		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   设备，就是 Looking Glass 的内存设备了。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i7. 修改 `/etc/apparmor.d/local/abstractions/libvirt-qemu` 文件增加一行：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     /dev/kvmfr0 rw,		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   以允许虚拟机访问这个设备。运行 `sudo systemctl restart apparmor` 重		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   启 AppArmor。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i8. `virsh edit Windows` 编辑虚拟机配置：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   1. 在 `<devices>` 中删除 `<shmem>` 一段：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        <shmem name='looking-glass'>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i          <model type='ivshmem-plain'/>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i          <size unit='M'>64</size>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        </shmem>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   2. 在 `<qemu:commandline>` 中增加下面几行：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        <qemu:arg value="-device"/>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        <qemu:arg value="{&quot;driver&quot;:&quot;ivshmem-plain&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;shmem-looking-glass&quot;,&quot;memdev&quot;:&quot;looking-glass&quot;}"/>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        <qemu:arg value="-object"/>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        <!-- 下一行有一个 67108864，对应 64MB * 1048576 -->		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        <!-- 如果你之前设置的内存大小不同请相应修改 -->		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i        <qemu:arg value="{&quot;qom-type&quot;:&quot;memory-backend-file&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;looking-glass&quot;,&quot;mem-path&quot;:&quot;/dev/kvmfr0&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:67108864,&quot;share&quot;:true}"/>		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   3. 启动虚拟机。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i9. 修改 `/etc/looking-glass-client.ini`，添加以下内容：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     [app]		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i     shmFile=/dev/kvmfr0		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i   		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i10. 启动 Looking Glass，此时应该可以看到虚拟机画面。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i11. （2023-05）如果你用的是 NixOS，可以直接使用下面的配置：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  {		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    boot.extraModulePackages = with config.boot.kernelPackages; [		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      kvmfr		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    ];		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    boot.extraModprobeConfig = ''		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      # 这里的内存大小计算方法和虚拟机的 shmem 一项相同。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      options kvmfr static_size_mb=64		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    '';		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    boot.kernelModules = ["kvmfr"];		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    services.udev.extraRules = ''		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      SUBSYSTEM=="kvmfr", OWNER="root", GROUP="libvirtd", MODE="0660"		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    '';		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    environment.etc."looking-glass-client.ini".text = ''		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      [app]		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i      shmFile=/dev/kvmfr0		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    '';		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  }		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
